\"}]'),(155,187,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s really something to have a tutor, though.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Well…\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Lain doesn’t seem like someone with a problem.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"No, no.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She doesn’t have a problem.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I just want to know more about her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She’s a very nice girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"She’s the kind of girl that keeps quiet even when something is bothering her, so that she doesn’t worry other people, isn’t she?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"You’re right.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"She is that way.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I remember too, that once when I tried to buy a treat for her for helping me with my homework, she refused.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I was a bit irritated.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Lain hasn’t been bullied at school, though.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"The kids there aren’t so bad there.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Really?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Well, sure. Do you doubt me? I don’t get bullied either. Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}]'),(156,188,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"But, One-chan, could you be my tutor, too? My grades aren’t so great.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’d love to, but I can’t because I have a lot of work to do at the university.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"If I find a good tutor, I’ll recommend her to you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"You can repay me by being really nice to Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Wow!\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"You really are like a big sister.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wish I had a sister.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m an only child.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Lain’s an only child, too, isn’t she?\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Does she have siblings?\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"My mom said something about Lain having a sibling in the hospital, and that that’s why neighbors avoid her house.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Lain is an only child.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Her parents are good, ordinary people.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I suppose Lain is sad to be an only child, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(157,189,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Diary? What should I write? What should I write about myself?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Today I woke up and went to school and attended class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"After school, I went to Touko to talk with her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She said that keeping a diary is good for me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This is to be read by only myself, so I don\'t have any idea what to write.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"…I came home and ate dinner and watched TV and took a bath…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"And now, I\'m writing this diary…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Reading this makes me blush!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Keeping a diary may be tough to deal with.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I want to give it up.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(158,190,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today, I went shopping with Kyoko.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I bought an earring and a bracelet.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But, I feel a little ashamed to go out with these on.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Kyoko is cute, so it is no problem for her to wear these.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I\'m not cute, so whatever I do, it’s useless.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I think I\'m lost on buying these accessories…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But… Kyoko said, “These suit you! You look cute!”\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I think it may be her flattery…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But I felt happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(159,191,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I went to the library.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I tried to look into difficult words that Touko used like “psychoanalysis,” “counseling,” and so on.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But, I couldn\'t understand these words completely.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Am I stupid?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"…I also think I say strange things sometimes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If I tell Kyoko and her friends about my trouble, they will think there\'s something wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It would be horrible if they felt like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I can\'t talk to them about my trouble…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(160,192,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Toko-san says that I don’t have to worry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Something is definitely wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"That thing I saw wasn’t a dream.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I know because I can see it when I’m awake, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 