nge.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I won’t ask her after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(165,197,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad’s been getting home very early lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He’s been asking a lot about school, and I’m getting a bit tired of that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom hasn’t been complaining as much lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if she’s being nice because I’m becoming strange.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This is sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(166,198,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"These days, I haven’t been seeing them at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe I’m cured.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"That would make me so happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if Dad and Mom and Toko-san will be happy, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(167,199,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I don’t want to keep a diary anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The only special thing that happened today was ‘that.’ I don’t want to see it anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why does that me keep drifting into my mind.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(168,200,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even after all these months, I can’t get used to it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I want to stop seeing these kinds of dreams.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I want to become normal.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(169,201,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad bought me a computer today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He told me to use it to take classes online when I stay home from school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ve been doing my homework.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ve been taking my tests.\", \"actor\": \"Lain