"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Sensei probably told him to come.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I couldn’t talk to him at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’m a little glad and a little sad and want to cry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I couldn’t even say “good-bye.” I hate this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(176,208,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today is a Sunday.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I cooked and did the laundry for Mom as a thanks for her taking care of me while I was sick.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"My food wasn’t so good, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if I did the laundry ok. Dad ate my fried eggs even though I burnt hem.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He’s such a good Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I think he might have been a bit rude to watch videos during breakfast, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder why Dad’s shorts are so large.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"They’re the size of my shirt.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Mom’s brassiere is big, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I wonder what that is about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(177,209,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve heard that men like womans who have large breasts.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder why.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I want to ask someone, but I’m embarrassed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(178,210,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m back to school after a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder if anyone was worried because I was gone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I shouldn’t have worried.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m glad that things are still the same.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I thanked Kyoko-chan for letting me read her notes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Kyoko-chan’s notes were full of goofy doodles, which was kind of fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(179,211,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Compared to my notes, Kyoko-chan’s look like a box full of toys.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her sketches of Kamiya Sensei resemble the teacher so much that I started to laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I showed the sketches to Mom, she told me to stop goofing off and to do the homework I have to catch up on.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom seems to be a different person from a week ago.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(180,212,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m so happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Tomo-kun wrote me a letter.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He just wrote to say that he’s doing well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m glad that I’m at least receiving letters, even though I can’t see the person who is writing me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I used to watch him, more than he watched me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m so happy to have a letter from him!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’ll have to write him back.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’ll have to get some stationery supplies to write him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(181,213,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"But… Tomo-kun had to have written everyone in class. He couldn’t have written only me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(182,214,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Tomorrow, I’ll buy Kyoko-chan a slice of cake to thank her for taking notes for me while I was away from school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s been a long time since we’ve gone to fool around in the city together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Going out right after school is a no-no, but everybody else does it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Why can’t I, every great now-and-then?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Oh, I’ll have to ask Mom for some money.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’d better buy Mom and Dad something while I’m out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(183,215,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Kyoko-chan doesn’t like me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Was I the only girl that received a letter full of doodles from Tomo-kun?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Kyoko-chan must be angry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"What should I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I got careless and for got to buy the stationery I needed to write Tomo-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Dear God, please let me and Kyoko-chan be friends again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I get a little bit happy when I think that I might be special.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Thank you, Tomo-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(184,216,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Kyoko-chan must be angry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I thought that she would go to the laboratory class with me, but she went off with Mayu-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It’s too late.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She doesn’t like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It wouldn’t have been like this if I had kept my mouth closed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Even when I apologized, she said, “why do I have to apologize to you?” She doesn’t like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She really doesn’t like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(185,217,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I have nothing to write in my diary today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(186,218,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Toko-san is a big jerk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(187,219,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I can’t believe what Toko-san said.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Nothing will return to the way it used to be.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m disliked.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Toko-san said to keep writing in my diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don’t need a diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t have anything to write.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Nothing has changed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I just go to school everyday as usual.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m alone during recess and lunchtime, and no one talks to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(188,220,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"How mean.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Writing graffiti on my desk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"As usual, Kyoko-chan won’t say anything to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I didn’t do that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ve never gone out with Tomo-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I felt like everyone was mocking me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I don’t want to go to school anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(189,221,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Kamiya sensei came to my house and talked with my Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom looked frustrated.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Kamiya sensei said that if I skip class any more, I wouldn’t be able to graduate.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad were talking about it after dinner.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Mom was crying and Dad looked very distressed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Am I a bad kid?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I want to disappear.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(190,222,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today Dad skipped work and talked with me all day.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He’s a kind Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder if I’ll make friends if I went to a different school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if school will be fun somewhere else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if I can go to the school Tomo-kun goes to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(191,223,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My teacher visited our house again today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It seems that I can go to junior high school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom bowed to the teacher many times.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m sorry, Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If I go to junior high school, I won’t cause trouble anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(192,224,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I went to school today, Kamiya-sensei said that I would graduate, and that I don’t have to force myself to come to school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Does he not want me to be at school?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Is he letting me graduate because he doesn’t want to see me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"To get rid of me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m never going to that school again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(193,225,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Is there a meaning to why I’m here? Does someone need me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(194,226,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I named a special gift Dad got for me today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I named it Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She’s another me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"My only friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But when I go to junior high, I’ll make real friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If I appear at ease and lighthearted, won’t other kids like me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(195,227,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I talked to Dad about computer connections.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He went through a lot of elaborate steps to set up my computer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We worked hard for about 5 hours setting it up.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Dad was reading lots of books about computers while we did it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Once we were done, Dad called Mom, and the three of us were delighted.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t think we felt so good together as a family in a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It seems like since I stopped going to school, Mom and Dad haven’t been as happy as they used to be.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(196,228,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Computer networks are amazing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No one can see my face from there, and I don’t feel embarrassed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I feel like I’m becoming a different me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There are so many people online, and they’re kind to me even though I’m just someone with a lot of problems.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m so happy that people could be so kind to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(197,229,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I surfed the net all day again today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m surprised at what an easy-going person I can be on the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"My name on the net is “Lain,” but it seems that they can’t tell from that that I’m a girl.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If something interesting happens, I get e-mails telling me about it right away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Everybody is friendly.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No one can bully me here.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"My eyes hurt after I stare at the monitor all day long.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But for me, having my eyesight deteriorate would be a good thing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(198,230,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Programs seemed difficult at first, but some of them got easier after I studied them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have time now anyway, so I think I’ll study.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It shouldn’t be any trouble.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad won’t be there to protect me forever.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ll borrow a book from the library tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I can study when I’m online, but if I’m online all the time, I might not be able to receive phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(199,231,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Maybe Kyoko-chan is worried about me. Well…probably not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(200,232,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I started a game on the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s called the “Mouse Game” You sell tickets to your friends and make money.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But if I start making lots of money, the other players will have a grudge against me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There will be people who want to kill me then, so I have to be careful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"At first I thought this was just a game, but it made me feel bad after a while, and I wanted to cry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"There was a questionnaire that came with the game asking me what I thought of it, so I wrote the company telling them what I honestly thought.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I guess they know who I am now and don’t like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I don’t like games like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’d rather play a game that everyone can laugh with and enjoy together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It isn’t for me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(201,233,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It was a graduation ceremony, but I didn\'t want to go.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Once I’m in junior high, I’ll go for sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I promise.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I won’t worry Mom anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"You took my clothes to the dry cleaners, didn’t you, Mom?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(202,234,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What does everyone think about me? Does anyone think anything about me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(203,235,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Spring break starts today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I haven’t been going to school, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I was at the library reading a book about UNIX, a guy next to me who looked about the age of a college student gave me a really weird look.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Studying computers is tough because there are many technical terms and difficult kanji, but I enjoy this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"There’s nothing painful about it, and it’s more fun than grammar or math.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I understand English better now, and I understand things better in general, but there are still many things I don’t understand.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I think I’ll ask Dad about some of this stuff.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if Dad will give me a weird look like the guy in the library.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(204,236,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I decoded a file that came today by e-mail, I saw the image of a dead infant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I couldn’t find the address the file came from.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder if it’s from the person that started that tasteless online game.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m getting scared to open my mail now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I can’t leave here, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"At least not until I enter junior high and start an ordinary life.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When I start junior high, and I’ll have friends and I’ll be busy, and I might not have time to come to the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I ought to study the net now while I still have time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(205,237,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was sad during dinner today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dad said that he has to go overseas because of work.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It was so sudden I was surprised and speechless.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He said he’d be away for 2 months.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I started to cry all of a sudden, and I lost my appetite.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dad looked worried, and he hugged me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"We’ll go to see him off at the airport tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(206,238,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad’s work seems to be really difficult.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I want to work when I grow up.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I want to be like Dad and live with self-confidence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(207,239,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"We’ll saw Dad off today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom seemed really sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We waved good-bye to each other for a long time as he took the escalator to the gate.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"On the way home, Mom took me to a restaurant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It was a nice dinner, but it was sad knowing that it will just be me and Mom at the dinner table for a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m sure Mom feels sad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"God, please let Dad come home safely.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(208,240,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom, do you feel uneasy with me? I know I’m odd. It’s ok. I won’t bother you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(209,241,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I told my net buddies about that gross e-mail with the dead baby, they said there might be a way to trace it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s not something I’m supposed to do, but I feel like a detective, and it’s a bit fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Whoever sent that e-mail is at fault, anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can retaliate a little.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m not such a good person anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What can I do if people say that there is something wrong with my character?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"After all, there’s something wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"“Strange” is what I am?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m strange, aren’t I, Mr. Rabbit?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(210,242,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"By following instructions I learned yesterday, I was able to access the host site.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was easy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Maybe I’m a genius at this kind of thing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I found some ‘footprints’ when I did some downloading.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m figuring out how to trace down that sick person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m going to mail him to set a trap for him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I can’t forgive someone who does something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m not going to cry myself to sleep anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(211,243,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ll solve it with my own strength. My own strength. I should be able to do that now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(212,244,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"That was it after all!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Within 2 hours of mailing that guy, I got a response.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was curious what it was, but I was sure it would be gross, so I didn’t.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I decoded it, set a trap, and encoded it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This way, that person will never do this again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(213,245,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I took the information on his host site and spread it publicly on a “mirror-site.” I didn’t look at any of the pictures because they’d all be gross.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The text of his site was gross, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m starting to worry if I trapped the right person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"What if I got the wrong person’s data or identification…I don’t want to ever do this again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It feels good to be able to do things others can’t do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Is there something wrong with me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(214,246,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s horrible, but I can’t do anything about it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Someone’s been reading my diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It’s been copied and displayed on an FTP site with a vulgar title.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I stopped it, but over 20 people have already read it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why did this all happen?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Other people can do what I can do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I think I’ll avoid the net for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to see what’s going on, but my diary might be on someone’s site, being reproduced right now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’m going to send an information-deleting engine into the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But what if whoever took my diary has the diary’s back-up information, too?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I’m sure the person who took my diary is that gross guy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"And if it’s him, he would certainly have that information.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I’m so mad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I can’t win this by myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"So this is what I amount to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I think I’ll consult Mr. Rabbit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I wonder what will help.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(215,247,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are the people who enjoy doing horrible things and hurting people really human beings like me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"But what am I?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(216,248,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I don’t understand anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Did that strange person know Mr. Rabbit?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He said, “Leave it to me, and forget about it.” Oh, I’m mad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I want revenge.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m not going to cry myself to sleep.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I want to forget everything I want to forget.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"The things I don’t like.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"The me I don’t like.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Can I do something magical like that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(217,249,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"School will start soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m going to be different this time for sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m going to be an ordinary, light-hearted junior high school student.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I hope I don’t have many of the same classmates I had in elementary school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad were talking on the phone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Were they worried about me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"That’s ok. You can both relax and not worry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I saw it again for the first time in a long while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Is it an illusion?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Is there something wrong with my mind?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I don’t care if I’m sick or not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I just want it to stop.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(218,250,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I started bleeding when I was brushing my teeth.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Could it be pyorrhea?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"My teeth were always so healthy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can taste my blood.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It’s a bit bitter and I don’t like it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I think I won’t stop bleeding and that I won’t be able to fall asleep.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Is it because I’m uneasy about starting junior high school tomorrow?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(219,251,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m different. I’m a different me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(220,252,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom came to the ceremony for the start of the school year.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"None of the kids from grade school were in my class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was relieved.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The teacher in charge was a nice person, and I made some friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I was assigned to a seat.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"There’s a different feel here compared to grade school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I can’t hang out with most of the kids, but I think I’ll get along with just one of the girls sitting next to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"She’s quiet, but that’s the kind of person that’s easy for me to be around.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It’s great to meet you, Misato-chan!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(221,253,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I feel like everything will go great now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"As long as I have one friend, I’m ok. Dad, I hope you come home soon!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(222,254,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I did a lot of things with Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She’s good at physical education, though I’m not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think I’m more into liberal arts.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan has been playing the violin since she was very young.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She’s even been in competitions.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She’s amazing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She’s good with computers, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I didn’t tell her that I’m into computers, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I wanted to keep things having to do with me and the net a secret.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"On the net, I can be the sort of me that isn’t so careful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(223,255,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I told Toko-san all about it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I talked about Misato-chan through the whole session.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Toko-san said, “you’re doing really well,” and I was a bit embarrassed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what Toko-san did for her extracurricular activities.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I think she’s good at physical education.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She said that she went to America for school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe things are different there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(224,256,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that she wanted to be in same extracurricular class with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m nowhere as good as her in music, and she said that she didn’t want to be in music class with me anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The people in the joint research group were very nice, but I wasn\'t sure if I wanted to join.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I thought I would join an art class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ve always enjoyed drawing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(225,257,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is really good to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"We’re always together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m sad when she doesn’t come to school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wish I had more friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if I’m being selfish.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Am I greedy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder if Misato-chan is ok when she is alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If I skip school tomorrow, how would she feel?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"If I tried something like that, though, she won’t like me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(226,258,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I didn’t want to stay home from school deliberately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"My head hurt, and I saw that thing again, so I stayed home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom had to go to work, so I was home alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I didn’t feel this way in elementary school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why do I feel so sad and tired now?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Does it have to do with Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe I’ll call Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"That’s expensive though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Mom might get angry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(227,259,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if Misato-chan is strong.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She seemed to be just fine while I was away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was a bit disappointed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if I’m too possessive.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe Misato-chan has friends aside from me, and I just want her for myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t like this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m just being blameful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m becoming a dislikable girl again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"In extracurricular class, I went to go buy sketch books with the rest of the class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"The pastels were very pretty, so I bought some and was drawing before dinner.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Mom scolded me, saying that the pastels were stinky.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I don’t mind their smell very much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I’m going to give my best to study and art.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Fight, Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(228,260,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I forcing myself to do too much? I’m not, am I?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(229,261,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I drew a picture of Toko-san and went to her office to show her, but one of the people there said that she was out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I guess she’s really busy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Dad is going to come back soon, and I’ve been feeling good lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can’t see ‘that’ anymore, so I think I’ll go back to the Net for old time’s sake.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I haven’t seen Mr. Rabbit in a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to say thanks for that time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I look pretty good when I’m making progress.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(230,262,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m not forcing myself to laugh. This is me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(231,263,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I saw ‘that’ on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I haven’t had a problem with that before.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why is it happening?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But I don’t have to go to the Net anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ve written a letter to Mr. Rabbit, so I won’t go back to the Net for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Things are going well anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It’s ok, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m not alone anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(232,264,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad came home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I talked to him a lot.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"About me, about drawing, about Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I talked and talked and talked until Mom said that Dad is tired and that I ought to hold off on talking to him until tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe I did tire him out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He was smiling as I talked to him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He brought me a Teddy Bear as a gift.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"He’s really cute.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"What should I name him?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Hmm…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(233,265,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if Dad has ever been so cheerful. Maybe people seem to change when you change yourself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(234,266,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad asked me to take a gift to Toko-san, so I took the gift to her after school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Toko-san seemed tired and slow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She didn’t even open the gift’s wrapping paper.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder why she was tired.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder what the gift was.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Could it have been cosmetics?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Mom has a lot of cosmetics, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I guess I’ll use cosmetics one day, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I won’t look very good if I used cosmetics now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Misato-chan looks grown up anyway, so cosmetics should look good on her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Oh, Dad said there were some extra presents, so I’ll take some for Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(235,267,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"A lavish present wouldn’t be good. After all, we’re just junior high school students.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(236,268,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan took a day off of school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don’t think she’s completely alone, but I was sad for her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I left drawing class early because I was sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I had Dad’s present that I wanted to give her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I hope Misato-chan comes to school tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(237,269,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I need Misato-chan. Does Misato-chan need me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(238,270,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan wasn’t at school again today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I told my sensei that I wanted to go see her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She said that she spoke with Misato-chan’s mom, and that Misato-chan didn’t want to see any visitors.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what the matter is.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Misato-chan had so much energy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She didn’t talk about herself much, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She was like me in that way.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But for me, talking got me disliked.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(239,271,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I want to talk to Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m cowardly, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Haven’t I changed?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Would it be better if a cowardly person like me dies?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(240,272,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan came to school, but seemed as usual, as if nothing had happened.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I asked her what kind of sickness she had, she just said that she had the cold.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Any way, I’m glad that she’s better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ll take her the gift I couldn’t give her yesterday.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I skipped extracurricular activities and went to an ice cream shop with Misato-chan instead.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It’s always fun to be around Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m glad she’s better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(241,273,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"This is the same as always. Nothing will change. I’m fine just like this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(242,274,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I was checking e-mails to see if anything came from Mr. Rabbit, I found a weird e-mail.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"This time it was a picture of a dead, naked woman, tied up with ropes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Strangely, it said that the e-mail came from Mr. Rabbit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mr. Rabbit wouldn’t do something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It’s that guy again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’ll let Mr. Rabbit know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I can’t believe this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Why would someone do this?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m scared to check my e-mail now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’d like to check my e-mails, but if I access the Net and I see ‘that’ again…I was getting better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’m not sick.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(243,275,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Right, I\'m really not sick.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"What Touko-san is saying… since she said it, it can\'t be wrong, right?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I should believe her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(244,276,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I have to do a drawing for a cultural festival soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder what to draw.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m not sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"One of the leaders said that it can be something simple.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder what.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"A drawing of Bike-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Dad, Mom?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Myself?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It’s difficult to draw people.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"If the drawing doesn’t look like the person, it’s embarrassing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(245,277,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What is Misato-chan going to draw? Lain? Or someone I don’t know?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(246,278,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that she draws with her computer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe I’ll try that, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ll ask her how to do it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(247,279,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Software is expensive.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"A digitizing tablet seems necessary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It seems that it’s better if there is a scanner.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It’s difficult with machinery these days.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I can’t afford this stuff with my allowance.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wonder if Misato-chan’s family is rich.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’ll talk to Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If I don’t have money, I can’t buy anything, but if I have a lot of money, I could do so much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"What would I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I could buy Mom and Dad presents, and I could do all sorts of things with Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It’s fun just imagining these things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(248,280,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"A person who works with graphics in Dad’s company is willing to lend me some equipment at a low rate.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I hope I can meet with that person soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Then I could have Misato-chan come to my house and she can teach me all sorts of things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This is fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder how many years it’s been since I’ve had a friend over.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’ll clean up my room and make it look welcoming.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder what kind of room Misato-chan has.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m sure it’s a very clean room.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(249,281,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My room doesn’t look very “girlish.” But that doesn\'t really seem to fit me. I understand.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(250,282,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"At school today, a boy asked to talk to Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When she asked why, he said that he wanted to go out with her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan didn\'t seem interested at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If it was me, I think I would have been a little happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I guess the boy was rejected.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He was kind of good looking.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Too bad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is good-looking and smart.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She could get a boy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Maybe she doesn’t want one.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"She looked really bothered.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Maybe she already has a boyfriend that I don’t know anything about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"That’s sad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(251,283,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s impossible to know everything, isn’t it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m not Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But if I was the person I used to be, I might have been that way, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(252,284,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I asked Misato-chan if she was going out with someone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She laughed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Well, after all, we’re together all the time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"When I was changing clothes for gym class, I noticed that Misato-chan had big breasts.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"My chest is flat.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But I don’t have ‘that’ yet either.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"All the others are really becoming girls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I think I’m moving slower than everybody else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(253,285,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The body doesn\'t matter much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"What matters is the heart.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"If my heart is perturbed, no one will like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(254,286,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to see Toko-san today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I asked her how much longer we should meet each other, she looked troubled.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She said that I could come over with the idea of enjoying myself instead of thinking of our meetings as therapy, but I didn’t want to have to explain myself to Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what Misato-chan is thinking.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don’t want to keep any secrets from her, but I’m afraid to tell her the truth.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(255,287,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You\'re busy with your own work, aren\'t you, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(256,288,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan gave me a present.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She said it was to repay me for the gift I gave her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan’s present was a CD of her playing a violin.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She plays beautifully.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Listening to her play is like drifting off into a dream.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She can really play.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She blushed a little when she gave me her CD.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"That was a bit unlike her, and it was cute.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I guess Misato-chan makes expressions like that, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It seems like there is more of the Misato-chan that only I know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"When I played the CD for Mom, she didn\'t seem too interested.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Maybe she doesn’t like the violin.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(257,289,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"We got a new PC today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It looks very expensive.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It’s small and round, but it’s very fast.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It’s different from the computers we’ve had before, but the man said that the applications are similar, so there shouldn’t be many problems.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I feel important all of a sudden, and happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Thank you, Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When I grow up, I wonder if I will find work related to managing information or something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’ve been studying hard and want to make myself useful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Still, I don’t want a job that only has to do with machines.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(258,290,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan came to visit my house today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom seemed to be in a good mood—sort of.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan taught me how to draw.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom came and checked in on us often.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Dad, Mom, Misato-chan and I had dinner together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It was great.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I didn’t learn that much about drawing, but Misato-chan said that she will visit again soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"We took Misato-chan back to home in Dad’s car.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She has a very fancy house in a rich neighborhood.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It was almost dreamlike.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Misato-chan’s mom came to the door and spoke with Dad a bit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"She was really pretty, like an actress.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I guess that a pretty girls like Misato-chan must come from beautiful mothers like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But only a girl like me could come from my kind of Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I’m sorry, Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But I really had fun today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(259,291,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I guess we’re different from birth.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"But if I was born there, wouldn’t I have been pretty like Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(260,292,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I drew a picture and submitted it to the cultural fair, but I don’t think I have much talent.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Compared to everyone else, I’m not very good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan does great.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She said that she was still mid-process with her work, but I thought it was great already anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She drew a picture of Pegasus, with deep blue skies.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It looked as though Pegasus was really flying.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I don’t think I could draw a Pegasus that looks like it is flying.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I think I’ll just draw what I feel like drawing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’d rather draw pictures of Misato-chan more than anything else, but maybe she won’t like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(261,293,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m a little envious of Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She can do so many things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Other than using the Net, there’s nothing I can do better than Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(262,294,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I tried to remember Misato-chan’s face and drew it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder if it looks much like her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I showed it to Mom, who didn’t have much to say.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Dad said it was good, but I’m still not very confident.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I think I’ll quit the cultural fair.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Today there was something about the new Navi that I didn’t understand, so I went and bought a book again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There aren’t many books about this kind of computer, so I didn’t have much to choose from, but I bought a book that has to do with command lists.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It’s based in UNIX, so much of it was familiar, but it helped me understand assembly, which I had trouble with.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I connected two computers so that they could exchange files, and called it a day.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(263,295,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I saw an accident on my way home today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Something fell at a construction site and someone died.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Cop cars and ambulances were everywhere, and lots of people, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It’s sad that someone died.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wouldn’t want something like that to happen to me all of a sudden.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I am…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(264,296,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I finished my artwork of Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was very popular in class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It’s very pretty and artful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I bet it will stand out and draw attention at the culture fair.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I used pastels and watercolors.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that I did a good job, but I wonder if I really ought to have done a painting of her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I feel that I haven’t expressed myself as much as I wanted in my painting.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What kind of painting should I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Misato-chan’s paintings seem like Misato-chan’s.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"They are gentle and pretty, and seem to have an inner strength…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(265,297,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Toko-san was that kind of person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She seems different from before.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could it be because she’s been busy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She seems cold and distant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I told her about my artwork, and she said to bring that up with people in my class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wonder if she was feeling well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Could it be that I’m a bother because I’m no longer sick and don’t need to see her?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Toko-san is a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"The sicker I get, the more work she has to do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’m sorry that I couldn’t help with your research report, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Just let me know if you don’t want to see me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(266,298,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I don’t want to see her anymore. I’m not troubled anymore. To me, Toko-san is…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(267,299,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad have been curt lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"My family used to encircle me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It seems to be coming apart now, since I haven’t had problems lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if they are busy doing things that they couldn’t do while I wasn’t well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I shouldn’t complain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They’ve been so good to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(268,300,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Doesn’t Dad love Mom? Someone tell me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(269,301,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s been a while since I saw ‘that.’ I’ve become an ordinary kid again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have friends; I argue with my parents a little but make up later.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m in an ordinary family.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Everything is ok, now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m an ordinary girl.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(270,302,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s good to be ordinary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"People won’t look at you funny if you’re ordinary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t understand the feelings of people who want to stand out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t have the confidence to want to stand out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But is it because I’ve become ordinary that Mom and Dad don’t pay attention to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is different.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She’s a friend of ordinary me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(271,303,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Now that I think about it, I haven’t been checking my e-mails lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I quit going to the Net because I saw ‘that,’ and because of the mean messages people leave there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that she goes to the Net, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Maybe I should exchange e-mail addresses with her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If she knew how active and outgoing I am on the Net, she might be surprised.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If I had her e-mail address, I won’t have to bother calling her by phone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Mom’s been complaining because I run up a big phone bill.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’ll talk to Misato-chan tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(272,304,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m surprised at how long I can stay on the phone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder if I’m a very talkative person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I feel like I can talk and keep on talking to anybody.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(273,305,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan turned me down.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She doesn’t like checking e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She seems not to have much interest in the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if she got harassed on the Net, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The way she turned me down was unusual.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It’s too bad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I thought she would be happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m a bit sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Misato-chan will talk to me on the phone, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"We can talk to each other anytime, at home or at school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"She ought to be able to visit the Net on her own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(274,306,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m being selfish to want to communicate with Misato-chan over the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(275,307,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I checked my computer today, there were about 30 e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I deleted e-mails if I didn’t know who they were from.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"No e-mails from Mr. Rabbit yet.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Didn’t my e-mails reach him?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe he hasn’t read them yet.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I checked the ‘news group,’ I found that many of the packets had dropped.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Eventually, the members were all people I didn’t know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I got an idea!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’ll join a news group that has art as a topic.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"There might be people there that are like me, and I can be a lot more outgoing on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(276,308,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The Net I full of men.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Aren’t there any girls?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t mind writing guys, but I’d rather write girls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(277,309,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"People talked of nothing but Misato-chan’s artwork at the cultural fair.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Our sensei’s prestigious friends came and were very impressed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is amazing!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is my best friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Isn’t that something?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m so proud.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But Misato-chan didn\'t look very well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if she is ok.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(278,310,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m somewhat frustrated.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Would I feel good if my artwork was praised like hers’?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Would I be embarrassed?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don’t know, but I’ll probably feel good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(279,311,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Kazami Sensei mentioned before class that she wants to have Misato-chan’s artwork presented at the prefectural exhibition.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s amazing because Misato-chan is still in 7th grade.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Everyone in class went to the cultural fair and saw Misato-chan’s work.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Even the older kids were really impressed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Misato-chan doesn’t seem too happy, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She seems different lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"If she’s troubled about something, I wish she would talk to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(280,312,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if that is obvious to Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe she doesn’t want people to fuss over her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Will I be disliked if I fuss?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(281,313,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if people on art sites of the Net are hard to please.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I got friendly and sent pics of Misato-chan’s artwork, and they said that it was plagiarism.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never do something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Besides, some artistic big shots saw Misato-chan’s work and didn\'t think it was plagiarism.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why then would it be?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I feel contradicted.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I don’t want to visit this Net site again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I feel like I am the one being criticized.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Misato-chan and I have been around each other so much that we can tell what’s going on with the other without talking too much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(282,314,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Does Misato understand me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(283,315,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"They decided not to submit Misato-chan’s artwork to the prefectural exhibition.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don’t know why.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Sensei didn’t explain why.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan has stopped talking and looks terrible.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ve never seen her like this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What happened?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m sad for Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(284,316,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I didn’t talk to her at all today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I hesitated to call.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could she be waiting for me to call?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But maybe that isn’t true.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(285,317,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan skipped school today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Some of the older kids in art class were spreading rumors.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"They were talking about Misato-chan’s artwork and plagiarism.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The kids stopped talking when they noticed that I was listening.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This makes me feel bad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never do something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Never.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(286,318,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I can’t call Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m frustrated but can’t do anything.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t have enough courage.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can’t imagine what Misato-chan would say.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(287,319,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan didn’t show up at school again today, so I took my notes to her home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Misato-chan’s mom came to the door, but Misato-chan didn’t.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Is she feeling so bad that she can’t even come to the door?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Could it be that she doesn’t like me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"That would make me very sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No matter what other kids say about Misato-chan, I’ll always be her friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I want to see you, Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(288,320,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I just want to see you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I won’t ask you any questions.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I won’t ask you about things you don’t want to talk about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(289,321,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I talked to Kasumi sensei today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I believe in Misato-chan, but I wanted to see what was actually going on.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The sensei said that there is an art magazine in America with a painting by a Japanese artist very similar to Misato-chan’s.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I didn’t want to see the magazine, but I wanted to make sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The picture in the magazine and Misato-chan’s painting looked alike.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They were more than alike.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I could not tell the difference between the two.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It seems that the Japanese artist who painted it was just a novice, and that it was the first time she won a prize for her artwork.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I searched the Net about it when I got home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Dad said that that the artwork was by a second-generation Japanese or something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never plagiarize.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Still, the paintings looked so similar.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But I thought that Misato-chan did her work before this other person submitted hers to this magazine.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I’m going to look into it and clear her name.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Sensei said that people often come up with the same ideas at the same time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"It was probably a coincidence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(290,322,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Couldn’t it be obvious that people see the same things and have the same ideas about them?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"If the perceived information is the same for two people and they think the same things about it, why would it be odd if those people produce the same impressions about what they see?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We’re all human beings, after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(291,323,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The magazine is called “Beauty of the Art.” It had a homepage, so I sent them an e-mail.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder if I’ll hear back from them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ll keep writing until I hear back from them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m going to get to the bottom of this and I’m going to clear Misato-chan of this plagiarism charge.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But I might see ‘that’ again when I go to the Net, and that frightens me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(292,324,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Could it be that I’m not changing?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"If I think that I’m not changing, I won’t change.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But I have changed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I won’t have hallucinations anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(293,325,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got an e-mail from the editors today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m glad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan’s artwork came first.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I saw her sketch over 2 months before the other one was published.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Could this sort of thing happen often?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The same picture at the same time, both by a Japanese, all by coincidence?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What is that other artist like?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I couldn’t find a home page for her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I wish I had information about her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I know that Misato-chan was right all along, and I feel much better now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’ll go to Misato-chan’s home tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(294,326,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is going to another school?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She didn’t say anything to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"We were friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"We were best friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"All the other kids said that she went to a different school because she was embarrassed to be found out as a plagiarizer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"They were saying nasty things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I can’t forgive them for that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"They’re wrong.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never plagiarize.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I found out for a fact that she didn’t.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Those kids don’t know what they are talking about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But why did she go away?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Misato-chan, this is horrible.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Will I never see you again?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"It’s too sad to lose you like this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(295,327,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Why do people spread rumors without knowing what they are talking about?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Don’t they care about who they might be hurting?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(296,328,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m alone again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don\'t want to make friends with anyone other than Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Making friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t know what strange things these kids think about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don’t care.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It’s all a big nuisance.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"School isn’t any fun anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"School without Misato-chan is no fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(297,329,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When will I make friends again? When it happens, will I have to change, too? Even when I’m me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(298,330,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to Misato-chan’s home today, but no one was there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She must have moved.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She literally left without saying a word.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This makes me sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Didn’t she think of me as a friend?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I guess Misato-chan didn’t think much of me after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I haven’t received any phone calls or letters.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If she really was a friend, she would never have left this way.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Maybe she thinks I’m badmouthing her like the other kids.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I makes me even sadder.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I was your special friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Wasn’t I, Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(299,331,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Would it have been different if I had called you then?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Couldn’t you have said that I was on your side?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was only thinking about you, Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(300,332,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was thinking of not seeing Toko-san anymore today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I told her about Misato-chan, she said that there are some things that people can’t say, even to those who are closest to them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Did Misato-chan go away because I was hiding things about myself from her?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Is that why she went away without saying anything to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Even if there’s something I can’t say, I would never do that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Toko-san and Misato-chan are awful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Nobody understands me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I don’t feel like doing schoolwork.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Am I a truant?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I don’t want to leave people behind.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’ve got to fight.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Although they say that I ought to study what interests me, the only things I’m interested in are Misato-chan and myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But its over.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I have to find other things that are meaningful to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(301,333,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad had a big fight today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dad never hits people, but he hit Mom today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom threw things at Dad and screamed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I was afraid and couldn’t do anything but cry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why did they fight?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They usually get along so well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Was it my fault?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(302,334,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Why do people around me become this way?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Is it because I’ve become ordinary?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Has it been this way, and I just didn’t notice?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(303,335,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I told Mom that I wanted to quit counseling.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She said no.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She said that I’m ok now, but that she doesn’t know if I will get worse again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ve been missing school again lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I didn’t want to face it, but Mom is right.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to go see Toko-san again tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I don’t want to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I have no freedom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m a patient.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’m a patient that always has to be looked after.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I don’t want to do this anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(304,336,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What is the meaning of my existence?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(305,337,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I think I felt the way a person feels when she wants to die.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was placed in the same class as Kyoko-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I used to think that I would never feel badly facing Kyoko-chan again, but I became the person I used to be as soon as I saw her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Kyoko-chan walked past me as if I wasn’t there and started talking to other kids.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m sure she talks about me a lot.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It can’t be helped.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It’s true that I’m the depressing, strange kid who misses school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to move to another school, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I want to disappear.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(306,338,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve been going to the library alone to read books.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s depressing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But its better than spending free time at school alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I have to distract myself with books.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(307,339,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad had another fight.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I felt so miserable that I couldn’t be around it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I ran away to my room.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Dad got worried and came to check in on me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dad saw me crying and apologized to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Why did he apologize?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Aren’t I the one at fault?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m the one that should apologize.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’m sorry, Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(308,340,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I the one at fault? What about me is wrong?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(309,341,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder what I did.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I came to, I was on top of the bed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought I went to school as usual.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Did I fall?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"All I remember is walking toward school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I asked Mom, but she didn’t say anything.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I feel like something awful has happened.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What happened?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I can see hallucinations in my dreams again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I hear all sorts of voices.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’m going crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I’m not cured after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"There’s something wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I have to see Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(310,342,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I thought I was better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder what happened.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why don’t I remember anything?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There’s a white mist inside my head.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Everything is mixed with everything else and I can’t tell what from what.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(311,343,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom said that she went to my school to ask for a leave of absence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I thought that I ought to feel glad that I won’t have to go to school, but I’m sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ve genuinely been separated from society.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I feel that I’ve been rejected by everyone, and I’m sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Can\'t I live an ordinary life anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dad won’t come home and Mom looks worn out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Why won’t Dad come home?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Doesn’t he want to see me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Doesn’t Dad like me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I want to see him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I fell asleep weeping, and saw hallucinations again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"It’s scary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I can see them whether I’m asleep or not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I can’t believe it myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I don’t understand it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I want someone to prove to me that I am the person that I know I am.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I want to see Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I want to see Dad and hug him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"It’s ok…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(312,344,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Will everyone I love become unhappy? Will they become unhappy because I feel love for them?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(313,345,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lately, I’ve been taking correspondence courses and surfing the Net day and night.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I start to feel sick looking at the computer screen all day.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Dad bought me this computer, though, so I want to study hard with it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom left the house with the keys so that I can’t leave.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Someone help me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I hate being alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’ll be a good kid.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Please don’t leave me alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(314,346,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My only way to communicate with the outside world is through the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I can’t use the phone because I have no one to call, but I can connect with the Net right away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I can connect with someone that I don’t even see.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(315,347,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even when I go to see Toko-san, Mom drives me now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s like she’s guarding me, and I hate it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I can go see Toko-san on my own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what Toko-san really thinks of me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I remember talking to her a lot, though I don’t remember what we were talking about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t care what Toko-san thinks of me now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m crazy anyway, so take down all the weird data you can about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I don’t care anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(316,348,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I Mom’s kid?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Could I be someone else’s kid?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"My hair color is different from hers, and her face doesn’t look like mine.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(317,349,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I looked for Mr. Rabbit on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He was dead.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We’ve been out of touch for a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He had an e-mail address, but he hasn’t used it for a year or so.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe he took a break from the Net like I did.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"We discussed things that weren’t interesting or useful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What I want is to find the image of the real me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(318,350,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Is my own physical appearance an illusion or an ordinary phenomenon?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(319,351,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad divorced.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dad hugged me on the day he left.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was happy to have him hug me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He was warm and gentle.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I won’t see him for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m ok with being Dad’s daughter.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m the one at fault.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m the cause.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I hurt Mom and Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’m a bad kid.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I don’t want Dad to leave.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Will he hug me again?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I’m sure I’ll see him again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(320,352,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(321,353,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I share this big house with Mom now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The weeds are growing outside because Dad used to pull them, but he’s no longer here.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom doesn’t say anything.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I enjoy watching the weeds grow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I watch them everyday.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The swing outside that I used to play on as a little kid is now covered with weeds.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It’s like a haunted place.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to see Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(322,354,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Only the weeds look lively. Did the swing die?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(323,355,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom got drunk and threw a vase at me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She was angry at the wrong person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She was wrong because she threw Dad away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But isn’t that my fault, too?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If I’m so wrong, why not kill me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If you had killed me, you wouldn’t have had to divorce, would you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You’d rather not have me here, right?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(324,356,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m beginning to dislike people who drink.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Toko-san said that she drinks, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Do people go nuts when they drink?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t like it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(325,357,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I found a doodlebug nest in the yard.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I watched the ants get pulled into the nest by their legs and get eaten.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"What does an ant think in the moment that it is being eaten?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Do they know that they will die?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I found as many ants as I could and tossed them into the doodlebug nest.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I didn’t understand the ant’s feelings.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There’s something wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Why else would I be so cruel?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(326,358,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"If I am an ant, who is the doodlebug? Is it this house? Is it the hallucinations? Is it me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(327,359,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to an adult site.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was ridiculous.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It was lots of photos of women in embarrassing poses.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can see that the man would enjoy this, but the women… I guess they’re doing this because it’s their job.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But there are women who send in these things voluntarily, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What’s so great about sending in embarrassing photos of yourself?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(328,360,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if I have wishes to do these sorts of things myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s creepy to know that there are a lot of people who watch these kinds of sites and enjoy them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad had to do this kind of thing for me to be born, and someday I’ll have to do this if I want children.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(329,361,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if psychiatry isn’t a groundless science.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"There seem to be all sorts of treatments and theories, but in the end, psychiatry doesn’t seem to cure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I checked out my own diagnosis on a news group, but only found some boring, unsatisfying answers.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if Toko-san is a part of this news group.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why don’t I access Toko-san’s research center?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’ll find some of her research there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m curious to see how she’s using me in her research.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(330,362,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m going to check out Toko-san’s research center’s address.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I haven’t done any ‘cracking’ in a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(331,363,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve been trying since two days ago until today, but I still can’t get in.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I could access her research center.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Data about the patients Toko-san is overseeing was available, but it wasn’t really data—just file names without information.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"When I checked the file reports, I could see that everything was communicated correctly.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But I can’t see the actual data.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It isn’t as if it’s in encrypted language.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Information about me shouldn’t be any more important than information of other patients.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"The only information I can’t find is information about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"What’s going on?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(332,364,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I an exception? I just want to find information about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(333,365,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to see Toko-san alone because Mom was sleeping in.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I asked Toko-san what she writes about me in her research reports.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She didn\'t give me a clear answer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"While Toko-san left the room for a while, I took copies of some pages from her notebook.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I thought that I now knew the research data Toko-san keeps about me, and that I knew what she does with it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I could see that she sends information about me to the research room, and that she sends a lot of it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Could it be visual data?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Auditory data?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I also noticed some writing that seemed to have daily entries in it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Could it be a diary?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I couldn\'t find that data in her ‘host’ page.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Toko-san tends to transmit her data late at night.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I’ll try to access her site then.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"She has a very big file about me that would take a long time to download, so I don’t think she’ll find out if I accessed it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I don’t think Toko-san knows much about machines and computers.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I feel bad because I think I’m tricking Toko-san, but on the other hand, I feel good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(334,366,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I found Toko-san’s diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s wrong to read other people’s diaries, but it’s fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m understanding Toko-san better now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m finding out that she’s just another human being.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I can see that she thinks of petty things, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Most of what she writes is about men.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Was my report this simple?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m disappointed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I felt like adding some of my own notes, but decided not to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"There is a periodical security check and it found out about my ‘cracking.’ But I think I’m ok.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I don’t think I left any ‘foot prints.’\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(335,367,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder how Toko-san would react if she finds out that I’ve been reading her diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It gets me excited because I’m a bad girl.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But Toko-san is wrong, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(336,368,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad’s been away for a long time and I haven’t heard from him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Has he forgotten about me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I want to see him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I want to be with Dad forever.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(337,369,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Do you really want to see Dad?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"What kind of person was Dad?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He was tall, he wore glasses, and he had gentle-looking eyes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can’t remember Dad much anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(338,370,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got some free AI software that lets me replicate voices and images.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I played around with it, and was able to create voices and images on the computer that look and sound like Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I programmed it to say several expressions, like “hi, Lain, how are you doing?” The voice is very robotic.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I think this is all goofy, but it makes me happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I think I’ll add some more features to it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(339,371,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s weird for a daughter to grow her father, but it makes me feel that Dad is nearby and that makes me happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(340,372,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I gave Dad a Japanese signature.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Do difficult kanji suit him well?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Just a voice with a text is boring, so I set up the computer so that I can see an image of Dad and have him talk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I guess there are limitations.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I programmed the routing devices so that Dad can communicate with the Net and receive feedback.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dad is studying the Net now, so he’ll know more dirty words than me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You’re a dirty old man, Dad!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(341,373,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It can recognize general and representative shapes visually through the screen.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dad has eyes now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Can you see me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Dad’s file size has gotten huge, so I’ve had to break down the information.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(342,374,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I decided to make a model of Dad with 3-D rendering.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I got low on buffer and the computer froze sometimes after bringing him to life, but it seems more and more that he is alive now, and I am happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m breathing Dad’s life into the computer Dad gave me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This PC is Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Now I’ll always be with him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Are you happy, Dad?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Oh!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I should show Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I bet she’ll be surprised.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But I won’t show Mom until Dad looks more like Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’ll have him scold her for drinking.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(343,375,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"In order to raise the speed of the 3-D rendering, I routed more energy to the CPU.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I increased the amount of the rendering engine’s memory to 12 Gigs and optimized the signal pathways.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m finding limitations, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The more I try to work into him, the slower he becomes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I think the prototype was more like Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(344,376,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I showed Dad to Mom today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She was horrified.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She looked at me and left the room without saying a word.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Maybe she thinks I made him to offend her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I should have thought more about Mom’s feelings.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m sorry, Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Do you dislike Dad, Mom?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I love you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But I love Dad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I want to see Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(345,377,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I talked to a student at the Massachusetts Institute of Technology factory who is studying robots.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I might be able to make the kind of robots he’s working on at the level where I am now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I might be able to take Dad out of the computer screen now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There’s a ton of data, though, and there’ll have to be cables everywhere.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ll be able to hug Dad again the way I used to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’ll be able to feel him again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(346,378,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I want an accelerator that will work in conjunction with protocol 7.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Do any of you have that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ll ask someone who is a friend of Mr. Tachibana.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Tachibana is a researcher.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(347,378,'ru','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Мне нужен ускоритель 7-го Протокола.\", \"actor\": \"Лэйн\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"У кого-нибудь он есть?\", \"actor\": \"Лэйн\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Я спрошу своих друзей из Лаборатории Тачибаны.\", \"actor\": \"Лэйн\"}]'),(348,379,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"People operate around money.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"They aren’t willing to give away their technological secrets to strangers too willingly.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder what they would think if they met me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m not interested in that stuff anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m just interested in Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(349,380,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Making artificial organs is very expensive.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It won’t be a problem because I won’t be spending money, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It’ll take a lot of work to make his head.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ll make his upper body first.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"In order to control the electricity, I’ll need to buy batteries and lots of cables.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(350,381,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I put an electrical generator in Dad’s chest so he can start supporting himself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’ve placed motors in him so he can start moving around little by little.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The electricity heats him up, so he’s warm and gentle, just like my real Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I was feeling tired, so I gave him a hug.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I held onto him like a little baby.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(351,382,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s a bit embarrassing, but when I’m holding onto the warm chest of a man, there is something that makes me feels very good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I had Dad touch me all over my body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ve never done this with my real Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(352,383,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I was being held, I felt like a real man was holding me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I felt warm inside and was excited.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t know if it was because I felt like Dad was holding me or because I was imagining someone else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This feels good, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Is this what I wanted my real Dad to do with me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I just wanted someone to protect me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(353,384,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"There is something wrong with me. I have no business criticizing Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(354,385,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve finished Dad’s arms and abdomen.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wanted to add his pelvis, but I ran out of space for him in my room.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t want to sadden Mom again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I have to find house where Dad can live.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I hate to separate from him when I’ve really just met him, but how will I buy I house?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Even if I had the money, no one will sell a house to a child.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’ll just have to find an empty house somewhere.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(355,386,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I found a good place to take Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s not far from home, and there aren’t many people around there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ll take Dad there tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If I take everything, though, it will be very heavy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"How will I do it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If I carry something that large, someone is bound to notice.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"How about the electricity and the cords?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It won’t work.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’ll need help.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(356,387,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today the construction was finished and the building was handed over to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder what he thought about not meeting his client directly at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Moreover, since it was a bit of a big effort, I wonder if that made it seem all the more suspicious to him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I decided to keep an eye on his actions for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It would be dangerous for Father to be exposed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(357,388,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today, I took Dad to his new home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I took tape media because hard discs are heavy, but decoding them will take time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I took Dad’s legs and arms over little by little in the meantime, so I don’t think I did so badly.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Luckily, Mom got drunk and fell asleep.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It will be difficult to visit Dad from now on, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(358,389,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wanted to attach Dad’s legs, but working on the lower body was difficult.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s creepy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wouldn’t mind if Dad only had an upper body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can’t remove these cables.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It’s creepy that Dad doesn’t have a head.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I put an empty artificial head on him for the time being.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He’s able to talk, but poorly, and watching the expression on his face as he tries to enunciate seems phony to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"This isn’t Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I failed, but what can I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(359,390,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Was the only part of Dad’s body that I cared about his upper body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe I didn’t even acknowledge his body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"In my mind, Dad was always bigger than me…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(360,391,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I walked past a girl I knew in 7th grade, but she didn’t seem to notice me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"We hadn’t talked much in school, so I didn’t mind that she didn’t seem to see me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I saw her school uniform, I was jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t think anyone remembers me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(361,392,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My uniform was at the dry cleaner’s.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom seemed sad when she went to the store to pick it up.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She went to the trouble of buying it for me, after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(362,393,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I e-mailed a kid that used to be a classmate, and asked her about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Isn’t the me that acknowledges my existence only living in this small body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t have an individual personality and I don’t leave much of an impression.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Nobody remembers me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"When I made Dad, I started to feel that my own body was pretty lame.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Wouldn’t I be me if I had a thought re-routing?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I don’t need a connection to reality anymore, and it’s not so important to know that I’m a human being who will die unless she eats.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It’s more rational to me to have Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(363,394,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad was having some trouble.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I noticed that he was starting to move around on his own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could it be that he’s trying to see me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ll always keep an eye on you, Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m connected to you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(364,395,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Is Dad really Dad? Is he the Dad that loves me more than anyone else?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(365,396,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Someone has accessed Dad. But who? Some prankster who found my host site?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(366,397,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I had a hallucination for the first time in a long while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don’t know who I saw.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The me in the hallucination has grown.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She is in elementary school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But she’s different from the person I was then.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She had conviction in her eyes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Was the me that I was then me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"This is no good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I can’t handle this on my own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’ll go see Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(367,398,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Maybe Toko-san doesn’t understand me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She asks, “Are you really Lain?” She just tilts her head when I bring up my medical condition.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t know why I’m going to see her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She seems frightened of me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Toko-san, it seems that you are beginning to not understand me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I haven’t been changing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(368,399,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even a me like that can’t remember what I talked about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I felt bad for Toko-san and wanted to help her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"And then…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(369,400,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was concerned, so I accessed Toko-san’s notebook.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I found data about me that I wasn’t able to see before.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I went ahead and downloaded and saved the information.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"These days I get unusually tired and see hallucinations.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It drives me crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m getting drowsy again although I was sleeping just a moment ago.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I have a lot of e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I don’t even want to look at them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m sleepy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But if I sleep again, I might see myself again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I hate this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Dad…\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(370,401,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"In the mail there was a letter from Mr. Rabbit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was bright and gentle, like he was before he went away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wanted to say, “Hey, it’s been a long time!” and write him, but I couldn’t.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(371,402,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What’s wrong with me? I’m like the me I used to be. Who am I?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(372,403,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"How did she find my e-mail address?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Misato-chan’s mail came to my private, hidden site.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She wrote in a familiar tone as if we were still great friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan and Mr. Rabbit both seem to do as they please.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I was waiting to hear from them for such a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wrote down their phone numbers quickly and sent them e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m still waiting to hear from them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Have they turned their backs on me again?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(373,404,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"A bug was found in the mail?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The dates and times of the e-mails are fabricated.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could it be a problem with the server?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ll have to contact the server.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(374,405,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom isn’t at home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Where did she go?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Did she run away?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Could she be drunk out on the street somewhere?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I called the police and asked them to investigate.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They didn’t believe me because I’m a kid, but they came to my house to check.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I want to tell Dad, but I have no way of contacting him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Only Mom knows where he is.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"A young police officer was badmouthing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"He said that Mom must have “evaporated.” Mom isn\'t that kind of person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I felt bitter and couldn’t stop crying.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I was so mad I absolutely messed up the police host site.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"How do you jerks like that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I protect people who are important to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(375,406,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve been getting weird phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I pick up the receiver and hear dead silence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Either that, or I get creepy weirdo phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I thought of stopping the phone, but Mom and Dad and Misato-chan won’t be able to contact me then.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I answered the phone as much as I could, but I got tired, so I pulled out the plug before going to bed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I wake up, I am afraid of hearing “Die, weirdo!” screamed from myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(376,407,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Someone is trying to irritate me. Why? Why would someone do that to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(377,408,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I awoke I was grasping a gun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The smell of death and metal woke me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t understand it anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m absolutely crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I got scared.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I took the gun, put it in a shopping bag, and hid it in a desk drawer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There’s a key to the drawer, but it isn’t any good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’ll hide it inside of Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(378,409,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom is missing and Dad can’t be contacted.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I went to see Dad robot he hugged me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But that’s funny.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"How did he know that it was me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Did he hear me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Could he tell by the sound of my footsteps?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I didn’t think he could do that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Something might be wrong with Dad’s development.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"At first I was happy and didn’t mind, but at this specification, there is something wrong with his speed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I wonder why.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Is there a reason I don’t know about?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(379,410,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"One of my neighbors is starting rumors.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Why is she trying to tell me about it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She laughs when I turn around.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"What does she want to do to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(380,411,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I decided to make a copy of myself and put it on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I replicated my voice and appearance in detail.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"For thought routing, I rebuilt a system similar to Dad’s, enhanced it, and dispersed it over the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This way, as long as there is a Net, I’m a person who will never die.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Just like Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(381,412,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s almost a consolation.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I know that what I’m doing is meaningless.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m wondering if the me in the Net will evolve in a strange way.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(382,413,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I spend over half of each day in a nightmare.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe the world of nightmares is reality and what’s called reality is a dream.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Maybe they’re intermeshed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"After all, I have hallucinations when I’m sleeping and I have them when I’m awake.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m starting not to know which is which.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"That girl become a junior high school student.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Her height is the same as mine.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It’s like I’m looking in the mirror.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But I don’t think anyone will see this girl.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"She couldn’t be seen up till now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"There’s nothing to be concerned about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(383,414,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I talked to the me on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She’s the same as me, so she’s predictable.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Because I’m me, I can imagine how I’m going to be.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I played with the me on the Net, deliberately making her angry and making her laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Did she think I was fun, too?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(384,415,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I told Toko-san about Mom, she looked at me with a blank expression on her face.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"There’s something the matter with Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She’s hiding something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(385,416,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Who? Mom and Dad are together? Toko-san, you know about my parents, don’t you? Who was with them?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(386,417,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I killed Dad today. Mom is next.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(387,418,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s been a year, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain, it feels good to get back to a diary after a long time, doesn’t it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"This is my count down.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(388,419,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain, what do you want?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Pleasure?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Excitement?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Friends?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What I need right now is someone who wants to know me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Toko-san promised me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"She said that she would understand me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She said that she would choose me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(389,420,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I took my last walk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"As I walked around town all day, I noticed Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She didn’t notice me at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She looked at me like a total stranger.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I can’t forgive her for that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t have to worry about her anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(390,421,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"From the standpoint of many religions, won’t I go to hell?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Who will pass judgment on the me on the Net?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"How about me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Will God pass judgment on me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"At any rate, I don’t need my body anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(391,422,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You people who want to know me, why do you want to know me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Will you benefit from knowing me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Am I for your research?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"For a stupid TV show?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(392,423,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Do I have a sad existence?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I guess people think so.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t mind that much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t need a backup.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"That would be useless.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The me on the Net also had a sad existence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"That’s why I killed her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Hey, did that hurt?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(393,424,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even when I’m not dying, my body feels fear.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mysterious.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Is the reason that I have the potential to feel fear no matter what I do because of what’s recorded in my genes?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t need those kind of genes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This is a small world that seems large only to parasites.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(394,425,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Do you know where I’m going?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don’t know either.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"That’s because I’m going to be born soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Will I become a more evolved human being?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If I think so I might as well think so.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"A human without a body isn’t human?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There are people who have bodies that aren’t human.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Is that me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m not human?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Lain is Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"What is it to be human?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"You’re human if you have a body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I’m me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Am I just conglomerated with my body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I need a body if I’m going to live in the real world.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Suicide would be stupid.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"It would be better to just die naturally.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I don’t need it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I might need it someday.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"That might be true.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I won’t need a body to live in the Wired.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I’ll need the recollections of the body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"How about the recollections of a body that grows older?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"My point of view may change?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Is there a need for it to change?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"There’s no guarantee that that will be you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Lain, what do I need to be on the Wired?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Existence and will.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"The rest is just data.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(395,426,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When this summer vacation is over I’ll graduate.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m a bit happy and a bit sad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will be returning to Japan one step ahead of me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I guess that can’t be helped.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He’s a brilliant guy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The people at the sponsoring research center wants to give him a new project as soon as possible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ahh, shucks!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m just jealous of him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I would love to start my own research soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Mmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But I have to graduate first.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"It’s too bad though, because I wanted to be with Takeshi-san until the graduation ceremony.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(396,427,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today was so cool that I couldn’t believe that it was mid-summer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I suppose it’s sticky and uncomfortable in Japan right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But why am I thinking about Japan all of a sudden?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(397,428,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"There will be a party at a friend’s home tomorrow, so I made an apple pie.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I gave Takeshi-san a slice, he said that with a pie as sweet as the one I made, everyone aside from himself at the party would enjoy it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He said that my baking had become Americanized.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It’s true that compared to the cakes and pies in America, Japanese desserts are usually much less sweet.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"At first I didn’t bake things this sweet.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But now, I feel that unless I make my desserts sweet, they would be unsatisfactory.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"If I get used to all this sweet stuff, I won’t want to eat pastries when I return to Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If I don’t cool it I could get fat and Takeshi-san won’t like me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’ll have to start another diet tomorrow!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(398,429,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s almost Halloween again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It’ll be my last Halloween here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Halloween surprised me at first.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"People would walk around in costumes day and night, having lunch and shopping as if everything was as usual.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"People would come out in frightening costumes at night.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I used to go out in a costume with my college friends too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I think Takeshi-san isn’t into that kind of thing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’ve never seen him in a costume.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It would be fun if we could go out in costumes together.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I wonder what kind of costume I’ll wear this year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"When I see Jack-o-lanterns on Halloween night, I sometimes wish I could just stay here and live with Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(399,430,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I took a walk with Takeshi-san along the Charles River.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I reflected on the four years that I’ve spent here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"At first I was elated, but things were tough until I met Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I think I’ve changed a lot since I met him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I suppose it wasn’t time for romance, but being alone was a downer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When you feel down you want someone to be around you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Bu it doesn’t mean that you ought to seek out a boyfriend thoughtlessly just because you’re feeling sad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’ve gotten my feelings hurt a few times that way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But Takeshi-san is different.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I feel safe just being with him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I think it’s the first time I’ve felt this way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Next year Takeshi-san will return to Japan and enter a research center there.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"What will happen to me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I would love to work in the same research center as Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(400,431,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The year is nearly over.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will return to Japan early next year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I won’t go back until I graduate, so I won’t see him for 3 months.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I haven’t been away from him for a long time, so I feel a tad worried.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if he is ok.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But the good news is that I’ll work with him at the same research center in Japan next year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m going to try to enjoy the rest of my time here as a student.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"At the end of year there will be New Year’s Eve, and plenty of fun events taking place!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(401,432,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hmmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Next month.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will return to Japan then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He said that he’ll celebrate my birthday with me because it will be before he leaves.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But knowing that he will leave bums me out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I go to the airport, I’ll want to cry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(402,433,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san went home to Japan today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I didn’t know what to talk about on the way to the airport.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was looking for words.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Did I make him feel uncomfortable?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But Takeshi-san is a gentle guy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He didn’t say anything.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He just held my hand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"He said that he’ll be waiting for me in Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"That’s right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’ll see him again soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(403,434,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got a letter from Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He said, “Let’s celebrate your graduation when you return to Japan.” I’m so happy!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is working hard at his research center.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ve been sad about him being away for a long time now, but that’s embarrassing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is working so hard.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to work hard, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I have to work hard and do research, and become a good researcher that others will be impressed by.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to go home to Japan soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will be waiting for me there.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(404,435,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I cleaned my room to prepare leaving for Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have so many memories and photos.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"They’re all treasures to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can’t take everything with me, though, so I talked to Mary about selling them in a flea market.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Mary seemed a bit sad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Don’t worry, Mary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m going to give everything my best in Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(405,436,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m home!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m back in Japan after 5 years.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Japan is great.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Living in America was good, but I feel at ease being back home.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m a tad scared, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When you come home after being away for so long, you start to feel singled out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I remember being insecure in junior high school, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I would be tardy for school and Mom scolded me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Five years sure went fast.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I had no time to be homesick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"But you worked really hard, didn\'t you, Toko?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Study, study, study.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But I made good friends and there were good times and bad times too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I had romance that didn’t work out, but I had romance that worked out, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Looking back, I wonder what about me improved the most.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I’m ok, I’m ok!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Have self-confidence and fight, Toko!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I start working at the research center tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I want to end all my worries to end today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"When I go to the research center tomorrow, I might see Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(406,437,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Welcome home, Touko.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m so tired today.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t like the air in Japanese research centers.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Why do Japanese research centers have this sort of feel?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The people entirely lack a critical mentality, and they are lazy.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They give you a prejudicial glare when you mention that you just returned from studying abroad.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wish they would cut it out.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Research centers in America weren’t like this.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I suppose they think I was able to study abroad because my dad has connections.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Everybody is so icy here.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"When I was in grade school, we were so welcoming of kids transferring from other schools.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Maybe we change when we grow up.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"This makes me depressed, but it’s what I have to face now.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I can’t live like I did in America forever.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"If I do what I’m supposed to do, people will give me credit eventually.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Ok, Touko?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Soon I’ll have my examination to become a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Until I finish that exam, I’ll have to bear with things the best I can.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(407,438,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You can’t be sluggish, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have to work hard and get moving at a good speed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Everyone is indifferent about me anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t care if I don’t become super-prestigious.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I want to do the kind of work that I can be proud of.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"That way, good results are sure to follow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will be with me, too, so I have nothing to worry about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It’s too bad that Takeshi-san’s research center is in a different building, but next week I’ll have a date with him!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m going to purr around him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(408,439,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Today I was able to spend the entire day with Takeshi-san like I haven’t for the longest time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m so happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I really, really like him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san’s research center has its own share of cliques and rivalry and it must be hard for him, but he just stayed quiet and listened to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I see his big smile that seems to surround me completely, I feel so much better.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m so simple-minded.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m the one who does the purring, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Sometimes I want Takeshi-san to purr around me, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Even if he wants to, maybe he can’t depend on me for that right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’m going to work hard so that I can become Takeshi-san’s exclusive counselor!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(409,440,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve felt poorly all day today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Why do the Japanese like to spread rumors?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was surprised to learn that people know I’m going out with Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wish they would stop whispering behind my back.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"For my coworkers to hear things and imagine what might be happening is one thing, but to spread concocted stories about me like they are facts is sickening.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They say, “Oh, those two must be having a lot of fun in bed,” or “she must be tired of having sex with foreigners.” You don’t have to talk like that just because you’re in the restroom.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Most of those people spreading rumors are probably from the 2nd floor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What stupid talk.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I’m sure it makes them happy, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Ahhhh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It makes me so mad!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Now I know why everybody looks at me funny.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"If you want to know about my business, face me and ask me about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But instead you talk about this stuff for everyone to hear.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Why the hell are you working in a medical research center?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Do what you’re here to do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san told me not to mind it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I can’t forgive these people, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Agh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I feel like wringing their necks!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"What gives?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I can’t stay angry at these people forever.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"But I feel rotten today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"I wish Takeshi-san were here right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"But I suppose it would just be a nuisance if I go to him with all this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"I know he’s very busy now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"I wonder if he knows that all these rumors going around.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Maybe he’s feeling lousy, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(410,441,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Agh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"At a time like this I want to have a drink and forget about everything!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I have a big test coming up and I can’t get tied up with all this stuff.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can’t let those jerks get to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ll talk with Takeshi-san about this after the tests.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Until then I’ll just have to bear with this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Good night, Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(411,442,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I received a phone call from Harumi today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don’t hear from her often.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was surprised to hear from her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She’s a bit lazy about making phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But I was really surprised when Harumi told me that she was getting married.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She always used to say how she just broke up with a guy and felt like she just wanted to die, or that she wanted to have a guy introduced to her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She calls so infrequently.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I was wondering why she called, and it was about marriage.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I felt sort of relieved and slightly shocked.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But when a woman is 26 years old, it’s not odd for her to be married or to have children.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Ohh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Now I’m feeling jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"That’s ok.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"When I go to the wedding, I’ll introduce Takeshi-san and make her jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Maybe I’ll get married soon, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I\'ll call Takeshi-san tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(412,443,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I met with Kanako, one of my “naughty” friends from college.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Good going, Toko!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought of taking her to Harumi’s wedding, but she said that she might not be able to because she is busy with work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"How unfeeling!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I haven’t seen Kanako since I left for America, so I really wanted to get together with her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Kanako asked if my birthday will be coming up soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She’s right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"They say that things go fast for a woman once she’s past twenty years old.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"How true.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’m already 27.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Harumi will get married in September.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I wonder what Takeshi-san is thinking.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"What will I do for my birthday this year?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Ahh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Maybe I will propose to him!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But then again, no.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(413,444,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I just passed my test to become a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m so relieved.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It’s stupid that I have to pass a second test in Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Still, I wanted to let everybody know that I passed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wrote Takeshi-san an e-mail all about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder if he is happy for me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if he will call me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I sure wish he would.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(414,445,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if some of those nasty prejudicial rumors will stop now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Silly me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It isn’t that I’ve been trying to change people’s point of view.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Why should I be worried?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Anyway, I can start my research now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to try really hard starting now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(415,446,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"As always, a research room is a strenuous place to be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Even though I’ve passed the test, I’m treated like I don\'t qualify as a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don’t care for Professor Takashima.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He won’t send clients my way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He leaves me with a lot of menial tasks instead.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He probably says to himself, “the girl who went to America can’t do anything.” That makes me really frustrated, Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If I were a man, I would get recognition sooner.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"My study abroad doesn’t seem to count for much.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It’s no time to be worked up about Professor Takashima’s little chores.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I will get recognized.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(416,447,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve been here 6 months, and Professor Takashima still won’t send clients my way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He gives me this nonsense about how there aren’t any clients that would be a good fit for me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Such lies.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He just wants to use me for petty tasks.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I didn’t come here to be his secretary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I hate this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ahh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I don’t like that middle-aged old man!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(417,448,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"For the upcoming Golden Week I’ll be able to take a few days away from work.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I haven’t had much rest since I returned from America.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m happy about the break.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ve been stressed so much since I started working in the laboratory.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’d like to spend the time with Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don\'t need to go traveling with him.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I just want to be around him.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want some comfort.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Am I being selfish?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(418,449,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I met my first client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She is a 12 year old girl named Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was uneasy at first because I didn’t understand why Professor Takashima assigned me someone so young.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But as soon as I saw Lain’s face, I felt at ease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I suppose it was because she was cute.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I had an unusual feeling around her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Anyhow, even if she is very young, she is my client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It seems that she is troubled by auditory and visual hallucinations and feels psychologically unstable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Could she be having trouble at home?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Could she be forming an image of herself from experiences in early childhood?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I hope I can help her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I hope she will open up to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I’ll try my best.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(419,450,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Yaay!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Tomorrow I’ll have my first date with Takeshi-san since I came back from America.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m so excited.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what to wear.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I better not wear anything too flashy, or there will be more rumors about me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I haven’t bought many clothes lately.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It\'s hard to go buy clothes at this time of day.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I can’t go buy clothes during my date.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I can’t do that in front of Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I don’t want him to get a bad impression about me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(420,451,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I had dinner with Takeshi-san today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Because we hadn’t seen each other for such a long time, I had a lot to talk about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I talked so much that Takeshi-san was surprised.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san couldn’t get off work during Golden Week, so we couldn\'t see each other then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I thought I would be a little sulky, but once I saw Takeshi-san’s face, I lightened up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He laughed and listened to all my stories.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He even gave me flowers to congratulate me for passing my examination.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It’s so true that women love to receive flowers!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I want this happiness to last forever.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(421,452,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Oh, I feel so good.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Getting together with him after all this time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think I’m getting a bit lewd.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But I think it’s ok to feel this way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I really feel loved.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It feels more natural than it felt when I was in America with him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"If I get married to him, I want to feel just like this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(422,453,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I met Lain for the second time today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She looked right at me and called me “sensei.” That made me feel good, and I blushed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder if I’ve become transparent to her already.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I must be an inexperienced counselor if I blush just because I’m called a sensei.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"From the first time I met Lain, I had an unusual sense about her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wonder what that was.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When I look at her eyes, I feel as though she can see right through me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if she feels that I am someone that can help her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I don’t remember myself being as relaxed as Lain when I was her age.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"She seems very composed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"A 12-year-old is still a child, but Lain seems like an adult.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"They say that kids are all getting precocious these days.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I guess times are changing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Ah!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Now I’m talking like an old woman.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Don’t let any hallucinations beat you, Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I’m going to make you well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(423,454,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today was very busy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was able to have lunch with Takeshi-san, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He didn’t look well today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He seemed fidgety and said that he didn’t have much time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if he’s very busy in the research 