ine\": 4, \"text\": \"I want to go do some shopping!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I need to buy a present for Harumi, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder if Takeshi-san will go with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"He’ll won’t mind doing a little shopping with me, will he?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(425,456,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I became emotional at Harumi’s wedding.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’ve never seen her look so pretty.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She said she was going on her honeymoon to have a baby right away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m glad that she seemed so happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I love to see wedding dresses.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Weddings in churches are so romantic.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There were over 100 invited people attending the reception.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’ve never been to such a large wedding crowd.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Oh, when will I be as happy as Harumi?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It was unfortunate that although there were many people at the wedding who knew each other, there weren’t many people for me to talk to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"And Takeshi-san couldn’t come.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Kanoko couldn’t, either.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I know that people living in a society like this have a lot of things they have to do, but I feel that they should make time to go to their friend’s wedding.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Ah, well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I shouldn’t complain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I’d want all my friends to attend my 