ause she knew that I like something with my tea.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I was very moved by her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What are you doing getting so moved by a client, Toko?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe it’s because Takeshi-san didn’t give me a birthday present.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"That was terrible of you, Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Lately I’ve been moody.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I suddenly become sad or depressed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Is it because I’m getting older?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"But how did Lain know my birthday?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Did I tell her?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I don’t suppose it matters.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"It’s the first time I’ve received a gift from a girl, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"It’s a bit embarrassing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Thank you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(433,464,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It will soon be Valentine’s Day.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It seems like a Japanese celebration.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It makes me think.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san didn’t even meet me on my birthday.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I just received a flower delivery a week afterwards.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"There were no phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I think he really doesn’t like me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I just keep feeling let down.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Here I am with some chocolate.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"How dumb can it all get?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But this is the end.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"What’s the use?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I give up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Tomorrow, I’ll place it in Takeshi-san’s desk drawer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(434,465,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got a phone call from Takeshi-san today!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"“Thanks for the chocolates,” he said!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"“I’m sorry that I was busy and didn’t call you back for so long,” he said!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I had been so worried and worked up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m a pretty simple person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m so glad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He doesn’t dislike me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"He really was just very busy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(435,466,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s ok for me to believe in it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(436,467,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got an e-mail from Harumi.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was all about her honeymoon, and it seemed like she didn’t care what was going on with me at all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"That’s fine.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But since you’re happy, can’t you involve me in your discussion a little?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Aside from Takeshi-san, Harumi and Kanako are the only people I confide in.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe I need more friends, but I don’t have the personality to warm up to everyone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"These are all my own personal problems, after all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It’s not time to be taking care of other people.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I think I’ll talk to Professor Takashima tomorrow and ask him to let me stop counseling Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But if I do that, I really will have nothing to do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"If all I do here is petty chores, I might as well quit being here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(437,468,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"A resignation.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’ve never resigned from anything in my life.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"This is hard for me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’ll lose my connection with Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But I think Takeshi-san said once that he’d like his wife to be at home.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Why am I saying these things?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe the truth is that I’m not a good woman.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’m not the decent person I thought I was.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Maybe I’m a fraud and my faults are coming out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I suppose I had self-control enough to manage myself so far.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"When I think about it, maybe I am unstable now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Lain is the one that seems to have it together.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"It sounds like a bad joke.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I’ve failed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"It’s not right for Lain to come for help from someone like me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"There’s no excuse for it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"It’s over when I start making mistakes concerning my work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I’ll have to discuss it tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(438,469,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It is becoming spring like.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain will start eighth grade today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She’s hallucinating less often now and has settled down some.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She seems to be feeling better.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I sometimes wonder if my counseling is helping her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"We’ve talked about many things, but in the short time I’ve known her, she’s grown intellectually by leaps and bounds.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Sometimes she asks me questions during our sessions that shock me because they are so sharp.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Sometimes I feel like I’m the client, not the other way around.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Maybe I’m worrying about it too much.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Your client is feeling better, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"You should be glad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(439,470,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I met a new guy who comes to the lab now and then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He works with our medical equipment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think his name is Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He seemed a bit younger than me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He stunned me a little.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He was kind of cute and I gazed at him for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I was happy to just smile at someone for a while, maybe because I\'m not used to being in Japanese labs.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Maybe he likes me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Hee hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Sorry!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I belong to Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(440,471,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I know that I should tell him that I already have someone else.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Somehow I don’t want to tell him, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think I’m being unfaithful.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This is no good.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"As long as I’m feeling dissatisfied about Takeshi-san, I will also feel unstable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"This isn’t good.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"As a counselor, I shouldn’t feel this way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I have to fix myself before I try to fix Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(441,472,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Oh, what a surprise!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"To run into Yoshida-kun at a place like that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought that it was weird for a guy to be buying underwear alone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Maybe he was shopping for his girlfriend.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I feel embarrassed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It was nice to talk to him, though, and I have nothing to worry about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I guess I’ve been stressed lately.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I sure ran my mouth with Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I think I bothered him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Well, there’s no sense in regretting it now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun does seem very grown up for his age.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"He surprised me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"He’s not as grown up as Takeshi-san, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"He said, “Toko-san, you seem tired.” He was gentle, and I was a bit touched.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"No, no, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun was just feeling sorry for you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Ohh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Maybe his girlfriend saw him talking to me and got angry at him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"He seems so cheerful at the lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"He said that he’ll bring some sample medical utensils next time he swings by.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I’ll get over my stress soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(442,473,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Oh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Just when I thought I was able to meet Yoshida-kun, I screwed it up!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He said that he was waiting at the department store, talking to the person in charge of health equipment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Oh, I’m such a careless person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He suddenly apologized to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun was probably angry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ahh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I’ve done something embarrassing again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"He was just bringing the health equipment he promised to bring.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"The machine he brought was like a toy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It’s used for relaxation.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I wonder if it works.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"It’s supposed to work best if you use it everyday.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I think I’ll start using it tonight.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I bet Yoshida-kun gets girlfriends easily.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"He’s such a good-looking guy and he’s tall.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"When he comes to the lab, all the women seem to really take notice of him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Oh, what am I thinking?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I already have Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I want to see Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(443,474,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lately at the lab, people seem to be looking at me more critically than before.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"If someone wants to say something, let him say it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Still, this bothers me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"When I glance at people, I can see them whispering and laughing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I suppose its just more stupid rumors about me, but I wonder if I’m the only cheerful person working here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I had my first date with Takeshi-san in a long time, but I was so inattentive.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It seemed like Takeshi-san had something to say, but I felt like I had a big hole in the middle of my chest.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What’s wrong, Toko?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Are you tired?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Lately, Professor Takashima has had me digging around for documents.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Maybe that’s worn me out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"He can have someone else look for documents.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"What can I do?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"That’s how things are done in Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"That’s how labs are in this country.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I think I should have stayed in America.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I’ll use Yoshida-kun’s health equipment again tonight.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Sometimes it makes me sleepy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I wonder if it really works.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I haven’t seen it advertised much.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I heard that it’s still being used on an experimental basis.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(444,475,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s always me that’s treated differently.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m the first person that’s noticed and called on.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I hate this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wish I could transfer to a different lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"There are many things I don’t like here, but I’m especially fed up with working under Professor Takashima.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He always looks at me funny.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He was looking at my breasts again today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I might be getting overly worked up about this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Maybe he’s not such a bad guy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"There might be something wrong with him physiologically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(445,476,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wish a guy like that would be dead.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(446,477,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m making a diary entry for the first time in a long while.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Even though I’ve missed making entries sometimes, I’m proud that I’ve kept it up for as long as I have.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Lately I’ve been coming home from work and going right to bed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Still, it seems that by using the equipment Yoshida-kun gave me, I feel rested in the morning even though I go to bed exhausted.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m still tired, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I’m psychologically tired.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Why do I have to work like a dog so that Professor Takashima can publish his articles?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It might look as if I have less work to do because I have only one client: Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It’s true that things are going well with Lain, and that may make it seem as though I have less to do, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But lately, I’ve been feeling harassed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Why have I been feeling so irritable lately?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I hate it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(447,478,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ll still keep fighting for you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Don\'t worry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"There must be some reason why you’ve been hallucinating.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what it might be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Things seem to be going all right for her at home.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"There aren’t any congenital injuries.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She sees images of specific things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"There must be a reason.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But what am I writing this down for?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I’m going to bed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(448,479,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Professor Takashima died.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He committed suicide.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I can’t honestly say that I’m saddened, but I’m not happy to see someone die.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The police and reporters came and asked a lot of questions, but no one knows why he took his life.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ahh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It’ll be harder at nights now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Why did he have to hang himself in the lab?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Still, I have one less reason for not wanting to work in this lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It may be imprudent for me to say this, but things will be easier for me now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(449,480,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’m glad you’re dead, bald old man. Did God hear my prayers and make him die?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(450,481,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today on my way home from the lab, I ran into Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lately, I had been so busy with helping Professor Takashima that I didn’t have time to talk to Yoshida-kun even when he visited the lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He seems to have been worried about me, and was waiting for me at the lab until I was through with work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I don\'t want him to be too kind to me right now, when I’m feeling so irritable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I feel like blaming someone for what’s been going on, and I feel that if someone is kind to me, my feelings for Takeshi-san will crumble.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun just quietly walked me home, but he made me very happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There was a “me” that was happy then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"No.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I shouldn’t feel this way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is the one I like.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"A good-looking guy was nice to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"That would make any girl happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san… I want you to catch me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I really am tired.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I better get some rest.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(451,482,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got a phone call from Takeshi-san after not hearing from him for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don\'t know why, but although we talked about the sort of things we always talk about, it was boring.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’ve never felt bored talking with him before.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It must be because I’ve been so restless.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Could it be that it’s over between us?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"That can’t be it, can it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(452,483,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain pointed something out to me today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I stayed up all night studying reference literature and had bags under my eyes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"How unsightly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"“You’re tired today, aren’t you, Sensei,” she said.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"“Shouldn’t you get some rest?” How embarrassing to have this come from a client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Lately, something has been very wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I don’t want it to affect my relationship with Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Is there a reason Lain needs to be hospitalized now?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It doesn’t seem like there will be any problems with her soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I think I should be examining someone else.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Lain is not sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"This is hardly productive research.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(453,484,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My head hurts again. I should go to bed early today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(454,485,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"This is a nightmare.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It must be a bad dream.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is getting married?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It’s just more gossip by those jerks in the lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san was going to marry me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But…that’s just something I believed on my own.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I know that we never made any promises.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But this is horrible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Why didn’t Takeshi-san talk to me first?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"He said that he couldn’t see me because he was so busy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Was he avoiding me that way?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Did he want me to get the impression that he didn’t like me and let me lose interest in him?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I’m… so…stupid.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I didn’t notice anything.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Why couldn’t you tell me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"If you told me I would have given up and let you go.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"That’s not true.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I couldn’t let you go.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I didn’t want to be his lover until he no longer liked me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(455,486,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"He’s not a careless person, so he must have been looking for a time to come and talk to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I just didn’t notice him because I’ve been so saturated with thinking about myself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But…I’ve been avoided.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"How stupid.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’ve just been thinking about being disliked.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I was clinging onto Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But I want to hear the truth from Takeshi-san himself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I can’t give up until I hear it from him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It’s all I can do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But if this is all just a rumor, I couldn’t say how happy I would be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’m sad…Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(456,487,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ve relaxed a lot and have been able to look at myself more clearly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"That has made it easier for me to write in my diary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I can finally see my surroundings.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The reason the jerks at the lab were laughing at me was because they knew about Takeshi-san getting married.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I’m understanding now that I’m the only one who had no clue.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I feel raw and bitter.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I feel miserable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I am sad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I can’t work anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I want to throw everything away and quit working at this lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I’ll quit counseling Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Lain will be alright without me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Won’t you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Who is going to help me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"He’s better than Takeshi-san anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"He’s young and kind and I want to be held by him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I wanted to cheat on Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"But that’s a lie, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Was I just looking for someone who would need me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I didn’t know what a weak person I am.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"I better head to bed soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"I’m sure there is a stronger Toko in one of my dreams.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"I’ll be different tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"As long as I go to sleep believing that, I’ll be…\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(457,488,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"These days, I’m on the computer most of the time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I didn’t used to sit in front of computers So often.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder if I’m unconsciously trying to connect with someone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Most of the rumors have fizzled down, but I still don’t blend in at the lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If Lain is like an ordinary kid, there’s no point to my research.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Why am I here anyway?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Will I spend the rest of my days doing menial tasks?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(458,489,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I can’t relax when I’m counseling Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Looking at her eyes drives me nuts.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Will you stop, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Don’t look at me like that!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Nothing’s wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"At least not in front of you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Lain looks at me as if she can see through me completely.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I remember feeling that way when I first met Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She can see that I’m using her as an object for research.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"No!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"How can that be?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"What can she know?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I’m the one with the problem.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I’m not present as a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"This can’t continue.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"It’s at times like this when I have to immerse myself on my work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"But when I was feeling unstable, Lain just looked at me, saying nothing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"She had a faint smile on her face.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Something is wrong with her!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"What is she trying to do?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Why can’t someone else take care of her instead of me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I keep saying that she isn’t sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Let me check one more time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"I feel so uncomfortable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(459,490,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I met with Kyoko-chan, one of Lain’s classmates from grade school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She’s in middle school now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She’s at a point of life when people start to take interest in many things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I was glad to have met with her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She was ordinary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She is ordinary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She goes out shopping with friends and talks with boys she likes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"She’s an ordinary girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Lain is not an ordinary girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"And who is Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Is she the same as Minako-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"That can’t be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I don’t understand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"What am I doing by following up on all these things and telling lies?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"This has nothing to do with my research.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"My job as a psychiatrist and a counselor was to diagnose and treat someone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"This existence called Lain seems to be a kind of vacancy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Does Lain have a problem, or do I?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(460,491,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I came face to face with Takeshi-san at the lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"My heart beat so fast!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wondered if he would pretend that he wasn’t married to someone else.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I suddenly froze; I couldn’t move my body or my face.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san smiled and just said, “Hey, you look really good.” Is that all?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Is that all you have to say to me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"The next moment, I found myself starting to laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san was surprised and ran away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I wonder why.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Why did I laugh?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Did Takeshi-san think that I went crazy?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Is there really something wrong with my mind?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Could this all be a dream?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Sometimes I can’t tell what’s real or what’s a dream.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Someone…help me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(461,492,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I’ll stop using the RML today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I think I lost confidence in myself because I depended on this device.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I am me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Lain is an ordinary girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is an ordinary man who found someone he likes more than me and married her, but was too weak-willed to tell me about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t like Takeshi-san anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(462,493,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I had dinner with Yoshida-kun today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I feel that I was more composed today thanks to him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder why he is so kind to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Maybe he’s heard the gossip going on about me and is siding with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Could it be more than siding with me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Could he be in love with me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I don’t know.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But I’m looking for love.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I don’t mean that I would want to love anyone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I liked Yoshida-kun from the time that I met him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"That’s not entirely true.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I’m just sad right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"It’s sad to be alone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I want someone to comfort me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(463,494,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lately I’ve been seeing bad dreams.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I dreamed that I married Yoshida-kun and that Takeshi-san was saddened by it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I looked at Takeshi-san and started to laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"These aren’t the kind of things that I would want.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe there’s a part of my subconscious where I want these things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But I don’t want my child to look exactly like Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I think that Lain is a good girl, but I don’t want my own child to be like her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Why, Toko?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I don’t know, but I can’t love her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I just can’t approve of it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"What am I really thinking?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I’m losing confidence in my own feelings.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"More and more I can’t tell reality apart from my dreams.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Is this a delusion, too?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Am I seeing hallucinations?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"No.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"That can’t be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I’ve become psychologically hypersensitive.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"You’re ok, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I should use the new machine Yoshida-kun gave me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Since he helped me, I should at least repay him by cooperating with his experiments.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"If I lose him now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"I’ll be in a horrible place psychologically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"I can’t go to a horrible place now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(464,495,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The ring that Yoshida-kun bought me…Could this be…he gave it to me without saying anything.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"But that’s ok.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I won’t make the same mistake.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I haven’t produced any research results either.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"My own pride won’t let me leave my work at the lab now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I asked Lain a dumb question today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I asked her, “Who are you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Are you really Lain?” Without changing her expression but looking upward, she said, “I’m me.” A question with such an obvious answer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Still, before even thinking about it, my mouth was open.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I wonder why.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I think Lain is probably tired of it, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I know.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"It has to do with the girl I’ve been seeing in my dreams lately who looks a lot like Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"She looks like Lain, but she isn’t her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I better straighten my mind out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Otherwise I won’t be much of a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(465,496,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to the cemetery to pay respect to Professor Takashima with the other employees.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It’s been a year already since he died.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"So many things have happened this last year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Rest in peace.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(466,497,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I understand myself less and less day by day.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was seeing strange dreams, but up till now I thought it was just because I was mentally confused.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But today, I had an auditory hallucination.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I’m not positive that it was a hallucination, but since yesterday, my ears haven’t stopped ringing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It’s as if I’m Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"“Orgel”?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What is it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It’s as if something is ringing inside my head.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Tomorrow I’ll go see a doctor that specializes in hearing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(467,498,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I was organizing the data I have about Lain, I started to hear the voices of researchers although there was no one there.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I couldn’t tell what they were saying.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I’m sure it was gossip about me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I thought I heard Yoshida-kun’s voice, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why did I hear him?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What’s wrong?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What’s happening to me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Someone tell me!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Someone help me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I can’t organize data when I’m like this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I’ll do it tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(468,499,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Tomorrow?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Will tomorrow be ok?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Am I going crazy?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If I’m crazy, no one would want to be around me, would they?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Who can I turn to for help?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I can’t believe anyone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Help…Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(469,500,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Toko: I stopped using RML.\", \"actor\": \" \"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don’t know why, but I felt I had to.\", \"actor\": \" \"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun, I’m sorry.\", \"actor\": \" \"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I sometimes worry that you stay with me because it has to do with your work.\", \"actor\": \" \"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I want to see Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \" \"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I want to see him and kiss him.\", \"actor\": \" \"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He knows that I feel this way.\", \"actor\": \" \"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want him to embrace me.\", \"actor\": \" \"}]'),(470,501,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I was organizing data again today, I had a sensation like the one I experienced while working with RML.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I experienced bright white flashes of light pulsing through my head.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought it was dangerous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It wasn’t as if I used the equipment incorrectly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I might have been mistaken to use it in the first place.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Was it manufactured improperly?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"This is dangerous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I have to tell Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Selling this machine is dangerous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(471,502,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"That’s it…if things continue this way, Lain will control me completely.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain must have seen all of the data here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why did she?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Why is all of Lain’s life history stored here?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don’t understand anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I can hear the voices again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Not just voices.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun and the workers in the lab are looking at me from a distance.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Why are you looking at me and laughing at me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Stop!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(472,503,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I going nuts?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I’m insecure unless I’m connected to the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why am I bothering to write a diary?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Who’ll want to read it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Probably…not me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(473,504,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s no good…I don’t know…what to do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun…you’ve betrayed me, too?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You were laughing at me from the beginning, weren’t you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"You and all those jerks in the lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I leaned on you and cried and told you what made me angry, and you took everything I confided in you and told everybody and laughed with them.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t want to believe this, but I caught you in the act.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You were the only person I had, Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"You were just a shallow man.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"How can you be so dumb, Toko?\", \"actor\": \"A Voice\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Who is that? Is someone talking to me? That’s impossible. Nobody is here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It’s me. Toko.\", \"actor\": \"A Voice\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Toko? I’m Toko! Stop! Who’s trying to torment me like this? Please stop!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(474,505,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain, can you hear me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I know that you are reading this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You creepy girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I will no longer treat you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I never want to see you again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(475,506,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Doesn\'t everyone wish for someone to die sometime?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"And you’re saying that you can’t forgive me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You killed Professor Takashima, didn’t you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I had nothing to do with it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The police said that it wasn’t me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They think it was a suicide.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Please.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Help me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I understand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"You’re a good girl, aren’t you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(476,507,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain…isn’t this enough?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Aren’t you content to see me miserable?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You’re watching me, aren’t you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Please, please, stop.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Forgive me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I can’t endure this anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I’m going crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Lain is behind all of this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"What do you want, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Tell me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I don’t know what the hell is what!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(477,508,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Stop, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"What did I do to you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Forgive me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Please.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don\'t want to go crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If I lose my mind, I can’t treat you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(478,509,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain, is suicide the only thing left for me to do?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Is there no other option?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Do I have to die?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"No!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don’t want that!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don’t want anyone to control me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Who does?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Aren’t you the same way, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"You were scared and scared and didn’t know what to do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Please Lain, help me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Please.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(479,510,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Who is “another” me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"There’s only one of me!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why are you saying these things that make no sense?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"We can think the same way and make the same judgments, it doesn\'t mean you’re human.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The only place where I exist is here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No matter where I go, I’m me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I am you.\", \"actor\": \"A Voice\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Stop it. Why is this happening to me? Is something wrong with me? No, nothing is wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(480,511,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain, how long have you been keeping an eye on me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Was it since we first met?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Or was it…I guess it makes no difference now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Am I going to be absorbed by you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Or can I remain me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Are you going to use me for something?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Can I remain me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(481,512,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I don’t want to die!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don’t want to lose my body!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I don’t want to throw my body away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I want to continue living in my body.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I have a tremendous fear of losing my body.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Maybe you can’t understand, but that’s how a normal human being feels.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Please, Lain, help me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(482,513,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Is it just that I don’t know? I don’t want to know. Stop it. I don’t want to know. Stop it. Please.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(483,514,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I can’t believe that you were that kind of kid.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain, it’s not too late.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Let’s fix this together.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But that’s not it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It isn’t about fixing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It’s about being reborn.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I am…\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(484,515,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It’s enough, now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Nothing holds meaning for me now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Crying, laughing, getting mad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Being betrayed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It doesn’t matter anymore if everything is a lie or if everything is the truth.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Could I have some more data?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to know you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(485,516,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I accessed your data, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"You cracked it yourself, didn’t you?\", \"actor\": \